Saurin haɓaka yawan cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) a cikin Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da United Kingdom, 1 Janairu zuwa 15 Maris 2020
Adadin adadin masu kamuwa da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) yana nuna irin wannan yanayin a cikin Tarayyar Turai/Kasashen Tattalin Arzikin Turai da kuma Burtaniya wanda ke tabbatar da cewa, yayin da yake a wani mataki daban dangane da ƙasar, cutar ta COVID-19 tana ci gaba cikin sauri a cikin dukkan ƙasashe.
Dangane da gogewa daga Italiya, kasashe, asibitoci da kuma sassan kula da lafiya masu tsanani ya kamata su kara shirye-shiryen su don karuwar marasa lafiya da COVID-19 waɗanda za su buƙaci kulawa ta kiwon lafiya, musamman kulawa mai tsanani.
A ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019, an bayar da rahoton tarin cututtukan huhu na rashin sani a Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 9 ga Janairu 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Cututtuka ta China ta ba da rahoton cewa mai haifar da cutar a matsayin sabon kwayar cutar coronavirus yanzu ana kiranta da cutar ta cututtukan numfashi mai tsanani coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Tun daga wannan lokacin, cutar da ta samo asali daga kamuwa da SARS-CoV-2 an kira shi cutar coronavirus (COVID-19).
Shaida zuwa yanzu ita ce kimanin kashi 80% na mutanen da ke da COVID-19 suna da cutar mai sauki, watau kamuwa da cutar hanyoyin numfashi tare da ko ba tare da ciwon huhu ba, kuma yawancin waɗannan suna warkewa.
A cikin kashi 14 cikin 100, COVID-19 ya zama mai tsanani wanda ke buƙatar asibiti yayin da sauran kashi 6 cikin 100 na masu cutar ke fama da rashin lafiya mai tsanani da ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani.
Mutuwar marasa lafiya da aka kwantar saboda COVID-19 ya kai kusan 4%.
A cikin wannan binciken, mun tantance yanayin da ke faruwa a cikin tarin cutar COVID-19 a kowace Tarayyar Turai/Ƙungiyar Tattalin Arzikin Turai (EU/EEA) da kuma Ƙasar Ingila (UK) kuma mun kwatanta su da lardin Hubei, China.
Muna kuma kwatanta adadin COVID-19 na yanzu a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da UK tare da na Italiya a 31 Janairu15 Maris 2020.
COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da UK
Bayan China, COVID-19 ya sami ƙarin yaduwar yanayin ƙasa kuma yanayin annobar COVID-19 a sauran duniya a halin yanzu yana bin wannan na wannan ƙasar.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, Babban Daraktan Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
A cikin fitowar 5 ga Maris na Eurosurveillance 2020, Spiteri et al. sun ba da rahoton farkon shari'o'in COVID-19 da aka tabbatar a Turai bisa ga ma'anar shari'ar WHO.
A cikin EU/EEA, Faransa ta ba da rahoton farkon mutane uku da aka tabbatar da su a ranar 24 ga Janairu 2020 a cikin mutanen da suka dawo daga Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
Ya zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020, an gano masu cutar COVID-19 a cikin dukkan ƙasashe 30 na EU/EEA da kuma United Kingdom (UK), inda daga 31 ga Disamba 2019 zuwa wannan ranar, an ba da rahoton mutane 39,768 da mutuwar 1,727, tare da mutane 17,750 da mutuwar 1,441 daga Italiya kadai.
Samun jimillar adadin da kuma yawan adadin COVID-19
A Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Kula da Cututtuka ta Turai (ECDC), adadin adadin COVID-19 da aka sanar a kowace ƙasa a duniya, wanda aka samo daga tushe na hukuma kawai kamar na ƙasashe Ma'aikatar Lafiya, hukumomin kiwon lafiya na ƙasa da na yanki da WHO, ana sabunta su kowace rana a 8:00 na safe.
An yi amfani da waɗannan bayanai don tantance yanayin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK, da kuma kwatanta su da na Italiya.
A matsayin wakili na yaduwar masu cutar COVID-19, mun lissafa adadin adadin masu cutar COVID-19 na kwanaki 14, don haka la'akari da yanayin yanayin COVID-19, a kowace EU/EEA da kuma Burtaniya, a lokacin 1 ga Janairu-15 ga Maris 2020.
Mun kuma gabatar da jimlar adadin wadanda aka sanar da su a kowace kasa a ranar 15 ga Maris 2020 karfe 8:00 na safe idan aka kwatanta da na Italiya na 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris 2020.
Yanayin COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da UK
Yanayin da aka samu a cikin kwanaki 14 da aka rage na jimlar cutar COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da kuma Burtaniya gabaɗaya sun bi na lardin Hubei (China) (Hoto na 1).
Ga EU/EEA da kuma UK gabaɗaya, yawan cutar COVID-19 ya fara ƙaruwa a kusa da 21 ga Fabrairu sannan ya ƙaru sosai a kusa da 28 ga Fabrairu 2020 (Karin bayani).
Wannan galibi ya samo asali ne daga saurin karuwar adadin wadanda aka ba da rahoto daga Italiya, amma duk sauran ƙasashen EU/EEA da Burtaniya sun nuna irin wannan haɓaka na yawan abin da ke faruwa na COVID-19 (Karin kayan aiki).
Hoto na 2 ya nuna adadin adadin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK idan aka kwatanta da na Italiya a lokacin 31 ga Janairu-15 ga Maris 2020.
Ya nuna cewa, a ranar 15 ga Maris da karfe 8:00 na safe, wasu ƙasashe 15 na EU/EEA da kuma Burtaniya sun riga sun ba da rahoton jimillar adadin masu cutar da za a iya kwatanta da na Italiya makonni 3 kawai ko ƙasa da haka.
Sakamakonmu ya nuna cewa adadin wadanda aka sanar da cutar COVID-19 na karuwa cikin sauri a EU/EEA da UK.
Abubuwan da aka lura a cikin yawan abin da ya faru na COVID-19 ya nuna cewa cutar tana ci gaba da sauri a duk ƙasashe.
Wannan duk da cewa ƙasashe suna cikin matakai daban-daban, bambancin martani na lafiyar jama'a na ƙasa, da yiwuwar ma'anonin shari'a daban-daban a cikin ƙasashe da kuma ladabi daban-daban don zaɓar marasa lafiya waɗanda dole ne a gwada su don tabbatar da COVID-19, gami da gwajin kamawa.
A farkon watan Maris na 2020, likitoci a yankunan da cutar ta shafa a Italiya sun bayyana halin da ake ciki inda kusan kashi 10% na marasa lafiya da ke dauke da COVID-19 ke bukatar kulawar ta musamman kuma kafofin watsa labarai sun ruwaito cewa asibitoci da sassan kulawar ta musamman a wadannan yankuna sun riga sun kai iyakar karfin su.
Bayanai kan shigar da masu COVID-19 a asibiti da/ko sashen kulawa mai tsanani a halin yanzu ana samun su a matakin EU/EEA don kashi 6% da 1% na masu cutar, bi da bi (ba a nuna bayanai ba).
Duk da haka, ya kamata a tattara su ta hanyar da ta dace don a cika bayanan sa ido na yanzu da ke mai da hankali kan adadin shari'o'in da aka ruwaito da kuma adadin mutuwar.
Wani bincike da aka yi a 201011 ya nuna bambancin da ke cikin gadon kula da marasa lafiya da kuma gadon kula da marasa lafiya a Turai, daga 29.2 a Jamus zuwa 4.2 a kan kowane mutum 100,000 a Portugal.
Wannan yana nufin cewa kasashe na iya samun karin ko kasa da albarkatun da Italiya (12.5 tsananin kulawa da kula da matsakaici na gado ga kowane 100,000 na yawan jama'a a 2010).
An bayar da yanayin yin samfurin da ya shafi cikar ƙarfin kiwon lafiya, tare da kimantawa ga kowace EU/EEA ƙasa da UK na yaduwar al'amuran COVID-19 da aka kwantar da su a asibiti da ke da alaƙa da &gt; 90% haɗarin wucewa da ƙarfin gado na kulawa mai tsanani, an bayar da su a cikin sabuntawa ta shida na ECDC saurin kimanta haɗari akan COVID-19.
Tun da yake har yanzu an tattara lamuran a wasu yankuna a cikin kasashen EU/EEA da Burtaniya, kuma asibitoci da rukunin kula da masu tsananin cutar yawanci suna ba da sabis ga ƙayyadadden yanki na yanki, ya fi dacewa a ba da bayani game da lamuran da gadajen kula da masu tsananin cutar a matakin Nomenclature of territorial units for statistics 2 (NUTS-2).
Kwarewar Italiya da kuma yanayin da ake ciki a wasu ƙasashe sun nuna cewa cutar COVID-19 tana ci gaba cikin sauri a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya.
Saboda haka, ya kamata ƙasashe, asibitoci da rukunin kulawa mai tsanani su shirya kansu don yanayin ci gaba da watsawar al'umma na SARS-CoV-2 da kuma ƙaruwar adadin marasa lafiya da ke da COVID-19 da ke buƙatar kula da lafiya, kuma musamman kula mai tsanani, kamar wanda ke faruwa a yankunan da ke fama da cutar a Italiya.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a cikin sabon saurin binciken ECDC na kwanan nan, hanzari, da himma da kuma cikakkiyar hanya yana da mahimmanci don jinkirta yaduwar SARS-COV-2, tare da sauyawa daga ƙuntatawa zuwa tsarin ragewa, kamar yadda ake sa ran saurin ƙaruwa a cikin adadin lamura na iya ba masu yanke shawara da asibitoci isasshen lokaci don fahimta, yarda da kuma daidaita martani idan ba a aiwatar da su ba kafin lokaci.
Binciken saurin haɗarin ya kuma lissafa matakan kiwon lafiyar jama'a don rage tasirin cutar.
Akwai ɗan gajeren lokacin da ƙasashe ke da damar ƙara ƙaruwa a ƙoƙarin sarrafa su don rage saurin yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 da rage matsin lamba a kan kiwon lafiya.
Idan ba haka ba, da alama tsarin kula da lafiya na sauran kasashen EU/EEA za su fuskanci hauhawar marasa lafiya da ke bukatar kula mai tsanani a cikin kwanaki ko makonni masu zuwa.
Cutar cutar Coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19), wacce cutar ta SARS (SARS) coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2) ta haifar, ya zuwa yanzu ta kashe sama da mutane 3,000 kuma ta kamu da sama da 80,000 a China da sauran wurare a duniya, wanda hakan ya haifar da bala'i ga mutane.
Kamar dai kwayar cutar ta SARS-CoV, wacce ta haifar da SARS a cikin dubban mutane a 2003, SARS-CoV-2 na iya kuma watsawa daga jemagu kuma yana haifar da irin wannan alamun ta hanyar irin wannan tsari.
Koyaya, COVID-19 yana da ƙarancin tsanani da mutuwa fiye da SARS amma yana da saurin yaduwa kuma yana shafar tsofaffi fiye da matasa da kuma maza fiye da mata.
Dangane da yawan littattafan da ke ƙaruwa da sauri game da cutar da ke fitowa, wannan labarin yana ƙoƙari ya ba da cikakken bayani game da batun bincike mai saurin haɓaka.
Za mu rufe abubuwan da suka shafi cutar, ilimin cututtuka, ilimin ƙwayoyin cuta, ganewar asali, magani, tsinkaye, da rigakafin cutar.
Kodayake har yanzu akwai tambayoyi da yawa da ke bukatar amsoshi, muna fatan cewa wannan bita zai taimaka wajen fahimta da kawar da cutar da ke barazana.
Bikin bazara a ranar 25 ga Janairu, 2020 ya zama abin tunawa da ba a taɓa mantawa da shi ba ga duk Sinawa waɗanda aka bukace su da su zauna a gida don duk hutun da kuma na makonni da yawa bayan haka saboda barkewar cutar kwayar cutar.
Kwayar cutar tana da matukar kama da kwayar cutar coronavirus (CoV) wacce ta haifar da barkewar cutar cututtukan numfashi mai tsanani (SARS) a 2003; saboda haka, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta sanya shi SARS-CoV-2 a ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, 2020, kuma cutar da ke da alaƙa da ita an sanya wa suna CoV Disease-19 (COVID-19).
Annobar ta fara ne a Wuhan, China, kuma cikin sauri ta bazu a duk fadin kasar nan da kuma wasu kusan 50 a duk fadin duniya.
Ya zuwa 2 ga Maris, 2020, kwayar cutar ta haifar da fiye da 80,000 da aka tabbatar da cutar COVID-19, tare da fiye da 40,000 marasa lafiya da aka sallama kuma fiye da 3,000 marasa lafiya da suka mutu.
WHO ta yi gargadin cewa COVID-19 ita ce babbar maƙiyar jama'a  kuma mai yuwuwa ta fi ta'addanci ƙarfi.
Dangane da PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), a cikin ƙasa da watanni biyu, an buga takardu sama da 200 akan COVID-19 gami da ilimin ƙwayoyin cuta, cututtukan annoba, ilimin halittar, ganewar asali, da magani tun daga rahoton farko a ranar 7 ga Janairu, 2020 wanda ya ƙayyade jerin ƙwayoyin cutar da aka ware daga marasa lafiya da yawa.
Wannan bita yana ƙoƙari ya taƙaita ci gaban bincike a cikin sabon yanki mai saurin ci gaba.
Duk lokacin da zai yiwu, za mu gwada gwada COVID-19 da SARS da wata cuta da CoV ke haifarwa, cutar numfashi ta Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS, fashewa a 2012).
Za mu kuma tattauna abin da muka koya har yanzu game da rigakafi da kuma hangen nesa na cutar da kuma wasu tambayoyin da suka rage.
A al'adance ana ɗaukar CoVs a matsayin kwayoyin cuta marasa mutuwa ga mutane, galibi suna haifar da kusan 15% na mura 4.
Koyaya, a cikin wannan karni, mun haɗu da CoVs na mutum masu cutarwa sau biyu, watau, SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, waɗanda suka haifar da barkewar asali a China a 2003 da Saudi Arabiya a 2012, bi da bi, kuma ba da daɗewa ba ta bazu zuwa wasu ƙasashe da yawa tare da mummunan cuta da mutuwa.
Saboda haka, COVID-19 na yanzu shine barkewar CoV ta uku a tarihin da aka rubuta na mutane.
