Fiva sau da yawa shine babban kuma farkon alamar COVID-19, wanda zai iya kasancewa tare da rashin bayyanar cututtuka ko wasu alamun kamar tari mai bushewa, rashin numfashi, ciwon tsoka, tashin hankali, ciwon kai, ciwon makogwaro, rhinorrhea, ciwon kirji, zawo, tashin zuciya, da amai.
Wasu marasa lafiya sun sami matsalar numfashi da/ ko rashin iskar jini mako guda bayan farawar cutar.
A cikin lokuta masu tsanani, marasa lafiya da sauri sun ci gaba da ci gaba da ciwon cututtuka na numfashi, da damuwa, da acid acid, da kuma coagulopathy.
Marasa lafiya da zazzabi da/ ko alamun cututtukan numfashi da zazzabi mai tsanani, ko da ba tare da halayen hoto na huhu ba, ya kamata a bincika cutar don ganewar asali.
Nazarin alƙaluma a ƙarshen Disamba na 2019 ya nuna cewa yawan adadin alamun cutar ya kai kashi 98% don zazzaɓi, 76% don tari mai bushewa, 55% don dyspnea, da 3% don zawo; 8% na marasa lafiya sun buƙaci tallafin iska.
An bayar da rahoton irin wannan binciken a cikin binciken biyu na kwanan nan na gungun iyali da gungun da aka haifar da watsawa daga mutum mara alamun.
Daidai haka, wani bincike na alƙaluma a 2012 ya nuna cewa marasa lafiya na MERS-CoV kuma suna da zazzaɓi (98%), tari mai bushe (47%), da kuma dyspnea (55%) a matsayin manyan alamunsu.
Koyaya, 80% daga cikinsu sun buƙaci tallafin iska, fiye da marasa lafiya na COVID-19 kuma daidai yake da yawan mutuwar MERS fiye da na COVID-19.
An kuma lura da zawo (26%) da ciwon makogwaro (21%) a cikin marasa lafiya MERS.
A cikin marasa lafiyar SARS, an nuna cewa zazzabi (99%-100%), tari mai bushe (29%-75%), dyspnea (40%-42%), zawo (20-25%), da ciwon makogwaro (13-25%) sune manyan alamun kuma ana buƙatar tallafin iska don kusan 14% -20% na marasa lafiya.
