Marasa lafiya suna da al'ada ko rage yawan farin jini na jini (musamman lymphocytes) a farkon lokaci.
Misali, an gano cutar lymphopenia tare da adadin farin jini &lt; 4×109/L ciki har da adadin lymphocyte &lt; 1×109/L, da kuma yawan matakan aspartate aminotransferase da viremia a cikin marasa lafiya 1,099 na COVID-19.
