An gano rashin daidaito a cikin hotunan rediyo na kirji a cikin yawancin marasa lafiya na COVID-19 kuma an nuna su ta hanyar inuwa mai banƙyama ta ɓangarori biyu ko rashin haske na gilashi a cikin huhu.
Marasa lafiya sukan kamu da cutar huhu, cutar huhu mai tsanani, da kuma cutar numfashi mai tsanani (ARDS).
Idan ARDS ta faru, kumburi da ba a sarrafawa, da kuma ruwa da ke tarawa, da kuma ciwon ƙwaƙwalwa da ke ci gaba suna sa musayar iskar gas ta yi muni sosai.
Rashin aiki na nau'in-I da nau'in-II pneumocytes yana rage matakin surfactant kuma yana ƙaruwa da tashin hankali na farfajiyar, don haka rage ikon huhu don fadadawa da haɓaka haɗarin faɗuwar huhu.
Saboda haka, mafi munin binciken radiographic na kirji sau da yawa yana daidai da mafi girman cutar.
A ranar 18 ga Fabrairu, 2020, bincike na farko na ilimin cututtuka na COVID-19 ya nuna rashin ƙarancin pneumocytes, samuwar membrane na hyaline, da kuma shiga cikin lymphocyte na interstitial, da ƙwayoyin syncytial multinucleated a cikin huhu na mai haƙuri wanda ya mutu daga cutar, daidai da ilimin cututtukan ƙwayoyin cuta da ARDS da kuma kama da na marasa lafiya na SARS da MERS.
