Koyaya, saboda yawan adadin rashin gaskiya, wanda zai iya hanzarta annobar, an fara amfani da bayyanar cututtuka don ganewar asali (wanda ba ya dogara da RT-PCR kawai) a China a ranar 13 ga Fabrairu, 2020.
