A ranar 14 ga Fabrairu, 2020, ƙungiyar Feng Zhang ta bayyana wata yarjejeniya ta amfani da fasahar CRISPR-SHERLOCK don gano SARS-CoV-2, wanda ke gano sassan RNA na SARS-CoV-2 na roba a 20 × 10-18 mol / L zuwa 200 × 10-18 mol / L (10-100 kwafi a kowace microliter na shigarwa) ta amfani da dipstick a cikin ƙasa da awa ɗaya ba tare da buƙatar kayan aiki mai mahimmanci ba.
Da fatan, sabuwar fasahar za ta iya inganta ƙwarewar da kuma dacewa idan an tabbatar da shi a cikin gwajin asibiti.
Saboda rashin gogewa tare da sabon CoV, likitoci galibi suna iya ba da kulawa mai tallafi ga marasa lafiya na COVID-19, yayin ƙoƙarin magunguna iri-iri waɗanda aka yi amfani da su ko aka ba da shawarar a baya don maganin wasu CoVs kamar SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV da sauran cututtukan kwayar cuta (Table (Table2).2).
Wadannan hanyoyin sun hada da magungunan da ake yi yanzu da kuma wadanda ake yi da magungunan antiviral, immunosuppressants, steroids, plasma daga marasa lafiya da suka warke, maganin kasar Sin, da kuma goyon bayan tunani.
An kuma bayar da shawarar amfani da plasma daga marasa lafiya da suka warke don magani.
Kamfanonin harhada magunguna suna tsere don samar da kwayoyin cutar da kuma alluran rigakafi.
SARS-CoV-2 yafi kai hari ga huhu a farkon kuma mai yiwuwa kuma ya kai hari, zuwa ƙaramin mataki, wasu gabobin da ke nuna ACE2, kamar tsarin narkewar abinci da koda.
Duk da haka, matsalar numfashi da rashin nasara sune babbar barazana ga marasa lafiya da kuma babban dalilin mutuwa.
Saboda haka, tallafin numfashi yana da mahimmanci don sauƙaƙe alamun da ceton rayuka kuma ya haɗa da maganin oxygen na yau da kullun, iskar oxygen mai yawan gaske, ba da iska mai ƙarfi, da iska mai ƙarfi dangane da tsananin cutar.
Marasa lafiya da ke da alamun cututtukan numfashi masu tsanani dole ne a tallafa su da extracorporeal membrane oxygenation (ECMO), wata dabara ce da aka gyara ta hanyar zuciya da huhu da ake amfani da ita don magance bugun zuciya ko numfashi mai barazanar rai.
Bugu da ƙari, kiyaye daidaiton lantarki, rigakafi da magani na kamuwa da cuta na biyu da kuma girgizar ƙasa, da kuma kare ayyukan mahimman gabobin ma suna da mahimmanci ga marasa lafiya na SARS-CoV-2.
An san cewa hadarin cytokine sakamakon yawan karfin tsarin garkuwar jiki ne a cikin marasa lafiya na SARS da MERS.
Cytokine guguwa wani nau'i ne na tsarin kumburi mai amsawa wanda aka nuna ta hanyar sakin jerin cytokines ciki har da TNFα, IL-1β, IL-2, IL-6, IFNα, IFNβ, IFNγ, da MCP-1.
Waɗannan cytokines suna haifar da ƙwayoyin rigakafi don sakin adadi mai yawa na 'yanci waɗanda sune babban dalilin ARDS da gazawar gabobin jiki.
Tattarawar rigakafi yana da mahimmanci a cikin maganin guguwar cytokine, musamman a cikin marasa lafiya masu tsanani.
An yi amfani da corticosteroids da tocilizumab, anti-IL6 monoclonal antibody, don magance cytocin guguwa.
Sauran hanyoyin maganin rigakafin cutar cytokine sun hada da daidaitawar amsawar garkuwar jiki ta hanyar kwayoyin T; toshewar IFN-γ, IL-1, da TNF; hana JAK; blinatumomab; mai hana siginar cytokine 4; da masu hana HDAC.
An yi amfani da steroid, a matsayin masu hana garkuwar jiki, a cikin maganin SARS don rage tsananin lalacewar kumburi.
Koyaya, steroids a manyan allurai ba su da amfani ga mummunan raunin huhu a cikin marasa lafiya na SARS da COVID-19.
Maimakon haka, suna iya haifar da mummunan sakamako masu illa, musamman osteonecrosis na avascular, yana tasiri sosai ga tsinkaya.
Duk da haka, an ba da shawarar yin amfani da gajeren lokaci na corticosteroids a ƙananan ƙananan-zuwa-matsakaici don amfani da hankali ga marasa lafiya masu cutar COVID-19.
A lokacin rubuta wannan, ba a tabbatar da maganin maganin cutar ba.
Koyaya, an sami amfani da maganin ƙwaƙwalwa tare da remdesivir, wani analog na nucleotide, don ya zama mai tasiri a cikin wani Ba'amurke mai cutar COVID-19.
Remdesivir wani sabon magani ne na kwayar cutar da Gilead ta kirkira da farko don maganin cututtukan da kwayar cutar Ebola da Marlburg ke haifarwa.
Daga baya, remdesivir ya kuma nuna yiwuwar hana wasu ƙwayoyin cuta na RNA guda ɗaya ciki har da ƙwayoyin MERS da SARS.
Dangane da waɗannan, Gilead ta ba da mahaɗin ga China don gudanar da gwaji a kan wasu mutane masu cutar SARS-CoV-2, kuma ana tsammanin sakamakon.
Bugu da kari, an ba da shawarar baricitinb, interferon-α, lopinavir/ritonavir, da ribavirin a matsayin yiwuwar maganin ga marasa lafiya da ke da alamun cututtukan numfashi.
Za a iya samun zawo, tashin zuciya, amai, lalacewar hanta, da sauran cututtukan da ba a so, bayan an yi amfani da lopinavir/ ritonavir.
Ya kamata a lura da hulɗar waɗannan jiyya tare da sauran magungunan da ake amfani da su a cikin marasa lafiya.
Plasma daga marasa lafiya da kuma samar da kwayoyin cutar
Tattara jinin marasa lafiya da suka warke daga cutar da ake kamuwa da ita don a yi wa wasu marasa lafiya da ke fama da cutar ko kuma don kare lafiyayyun mutane daga kamuwa da cutar na da dogon tarihi.
Hakika, marasa lafiya da suka warke sukan sami matakan rigakafi da yawa akan kwayar cutar a cikin jinin su.
Kwayoyin rigakafi sune immunoglobulin (Ig) wanda kwayoyin B suke samarwa don yaƙar ƙwayoyin cuta da sauran abubuwan da ke baƙo kuma suna gane ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin cuta na musamman a cikin ƙwayoyin cuta kuma suna kawar da su kai tsaye.
Bisa wannan, an tattara plasma daga jinin ƙungiyar marasa lafiya waɗanda suka warke daga COVID-19 kuma an yi wa marasa lafiya 10 masu rauni allurar.
Alamomin su sun inganta cikin sa'o'i 24, tare da rage ƙonewa da nauyin kwayar cutar da ingantaccen iskar oxygen a cikin jini.
Koyaya, tabbatarwa da bayani sun zama dole don ba da shawarar hanyar don amfani da manyan hanyoyin kafin a ci gaba da samar da takamaiman hanyoyin magani.
Bugu da kari, saboda tasirin warkewa, wasu raunin da ke tattare da plasma ya kamata a yi la'akari da hankali.
Misali, kwayoyin cutar na iya kara karfin garkuwar jiki da haifar da cutar sakin cytokine, wanda ke da barazanar barazanar rayuwa.
Yawan kwayar cutar a cikin jini yawanci yana da ƙarancin gaske, kuma buƙatar plasma yana da yawa don kula da marasa lafiya masu tsanani.
Yana da wuya a samar da ƙayyadaddun ƙwayoyin cuta da sauri don yaƙi da cutar ta duniya.
Saboda haka, ya fi mahimmanci da amfani a ware kwayoyin B daga marasa lafiya da aka warke da kuma gano lambobin kwayoyin halittar da ke ɓoye ƙwayoyin cuta masu tasiri ko kuma bincika ƙwayoyin cuta masu tasiri game da muhimman sunadarai na kwayar cutar.
Ta wannan hanyar, za mu iya ƙara yawan samar da ƙwayoyin cuta.
