Asalin kwayar cutar kwayar cutar mutum
Juyin halitta da daidaitawa sun kori co-evolution na coronaviruses (CoVs) da masu karɓar bakinsu, gami da mutane, na dubban shekaru.
Kafin shekara ta 2003, an san CoVs na mutum biyu (HCoVs) da ke haifar da rashin lafiya mai sauƙi, kamar sanyi.
Cutar da ke haifar da cutar sankara mai tsanani (SARS) da cutar sankara ta Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS) sun jujjuya tsabar kudin don bayyana yadda cutar HCoV mai barazana da rai za ta iya zama.
Bayyanuwar SARS-CoV-2 a tsakiyar China a ƙarshen 2019 ya sake tura CoVs cikin haske kuma ya ba mu mamaki tare da babban watsawa amma rage cututtukan cututtukan idan aka kwatanta da ɗan'uwanta SARS-CoV.
Cutar HCoV cuta ce ta zoonosis kuma fahimtar asalin zoonotic na HCoVs zai taimaka mana sosai.
Yawancin HCoVs sun samo asali ne daga jemage inda ba su da cutar.
An kuma san matsakaicin mai karɓar bakararren wasu HCoVs.
Gano dabbobi masu gida suna da tasirin kai tsaye ga rigakafin cututtukan mutane.
Binciken hulɗar CoV-host a cikin dabbobi na iya kuma samun mahimman bayanai game da cutar ta CoV a cikin mutane.
A cikin wannan bita, muna gabatar da bayyani na ilimin da ake da shi game da HCoVs bakwai, tare da mai da hankali kan tarihin gano su da kuma asalinsu na zoonotic da kuma watsawa tsakanin jinsuna.
Abu mai mahimmanci, muna kwatanta da kuma bambanta HCoVs daban-daban daga hangen nesa na juyin halittar kwayar cuta da sake haɗuwa da kwayoyin halitta.
Ana tattauna cutar ta CoV ta 2019 (COVID-19) a halin yanzu a cikin wannan mahallin.
Bugu da kari, an kuma nuna bukatun da ake bukata don samun nasarar sauya mai gida da kuma tasirin juyin halittar kwayar cutar akan tsananin cutar.
Coronaviruses (CoVs) na cikin iyalin Coronaviridae, wanda ya ƙunshi rukuni na enveloped, mai kyau-mai ji, single-stranded RNA ƙwayoyin cuta.
Wadannan ƙwayoyin cuta da ke ɗauke da mafi girman kwayar halittar jini na 26 zuwa 32 kilobases a tsakanin ƙwayoyin RNA an kira su CoVs saboda yanayin su na kambi a ƙarƙashin microscope na lantarki.
A tsarin, CoVs suna da kwayoyin halittar da ba a rarraba su ba waɗanda ke da irin wannan ƙungiyar.
Kimanin kashi biyu bisa uku na kwayar halitta suna dauke da manyan bangarori biyu masu buɗewa (ORF1a da ORF1b), waɗanda aka fassara zuwa polyproteins pp1a da pp1ab replicase.
Ana kara sarrafa polyproteins don samar da sunadarai 16 wadanda ba na tsari ba, wadanda aka ayyana nsp1 ~ 16.
Sauran ɓangaren kwayoyin halittar yana ƙunshe da ORFs don sunadarai masu tsari, gami da ƙwanƙwasa (S), ambulaf (E), membrane (M) da nucleoprotein (N).
Hakanan akwai wasu nau'ikan CoVs daban-daban da ke yin amfani da sunadarai masu amfani da jinsin.
Dangane da bambanci a cikin jerin sunayen sunadarai, an rarraba CoVs zuwa rukuni huɗu (alpha-CoV, beta-CoV, gamma-CoV da delta-CoV), daga cikinsu beta-CoV rukuni ya ƙunshi yawancin HCoVs kuma an rarraba shi zuwa rukuni huɗu (A, B, C da D).
Shaida ta phylogenetic ta nuna cewa baraguwa da rodents suna aiki ne a matsayin tushen kwayar halittar yawancin alpha-CoVs da beta-CoVs, yayin da tsuntsaye su ne babban tanadin gamma-CoVs da delta-CoVs.
A cikin dubunnan shekaru, CoVs sun ci gaba da ƙetare shingen nau'in kuma wasu sun fito a matsayin mahimman ƙwayoyin cuta na ɗan adam.
Ya zuwa yanzu, an san CoVs na mutum bakwai (HCoVs).
Daga cikinsu HCoV-229E da HCoV-NL63 sune alpha-CoVs.
Sauran beta-CoVs guda biyar sun hada da HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, mai saurin numfashi mai saurin numfashi coronavirus (SARS-CoV), coronavirus na numfashi na Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS-CoV) da SARS-CoV-2.
HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 da HCoV-NL63 yawanci suna haifar da alamun rashin lafiya, kamar sanyi da/ko gudawa.
Sabanin haka, SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV da SARS-CoV-2 da aka gano kwanan nan suna da cutar sosai, suna haifar da mummunan cututtukan ƙananan hanyoyin numfashi a cikin marasa lafiya da yawa tare da mafi girman damar haɓaka cutar cututtukan numfashi mai tsanani (ARDS) da bayyanar cututtukan ƙwayar cuta.
An ware nau'in HCoV-229E na farko, B814, daga ruwan hanci na marasa lafiya da ke fama da mura a tsakiyar shekarun 1960.
Tun daga wannan lokacin, an sami ƙarin ilimi ta hanyar zurfin bincike kan HCoV-229E da HCoV-OC43, duka biyun suna haifar da alamun iyakancewa.
Tabbas, an yarda da ra'ayin cewa kamuwa da HCoVs gabaɗaya ba shi da lahani har zuwa barkewar SARS.
Cutar SARS da ta faru a 2003 tana daya daga cikin mafi munin a tarihin yanzu, ta kamu da mutane sama da 8,000 tare da mummunan mutuwar mutum kusan 10%.
