Sabuwar HCoV (2019-nCoV) ta 2019, wacce daga baya aka sake masa suna SARS-CoV-2, ita ce mai haifar da cutar cutar kwayar cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19), wacce ta dauki rayukan mutane sama da 3,120 kuma ta harba mutane sama da 91,000 a ranar 3 ga Maris, 2020.
An yi ƙararrawa kuma dole ne duniya ta shirya don annobar SARS-CoV-2 da ke zuwa.
