Ana buƙatar sabunta ka'idojin bincike na COVID-19  wanda ake zargi da cutar  da  wanda aka tabbatar da cutar 
A ranar 6 ga Fabrairun 2020, ƙungiyarmu ta buga jagorar shawara mai sauri don ganewar asali da magani na cutar 2019 novel coronavirus (2019-nCoV), kuma wannan jagorar ta ba da kwarewarmu kuma ta ba da kyakkyawar tunani don yaƙi da wannan cutar a duniya.
Koyaya, cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19) sabuwar cuta ce, wayar da kai da iliminmu suna ƙaruwa a hankali bisa ga binciken bincike da ke gudana da kuma ƙwarewar aikin asibiti; saboda haka, dabarun bincike da magani suma ana ci gaba da sabunta su.
A cikin wannan wasikar, mun amsa wata tsokaci kan ka'idarmu kuma mun samar da sabbin ka'idojin bincike na "mai yiwuwa" da "tabbatarwa" bisa ga sabon ka'idojin bincike da magani na COVID-19 (juzu'i na bakwai) wanda Kwamitin Lafiya na Kasa na Jamhuriyar Jama'ar Sin ya bayar.
A watan Disamba na 2019, sabon kwayar cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (2019-nCoV) ta haifar da barkewar cutar, wanda yanzu an sanya masa suna a hukumance a matsayin cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19) kuma an sanya wa kwayar cutar suna mai suna coronavirus 2 mai saurin numfashi mai saurin kamuwa da cuta (SARS-CoV-2).
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, WHO ta bayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
Domin yaki da cutar SARS-CoV-2, ƙungiyarmu ta haɓaka jagorar shawara mai sauri kuma an buga ta kan layi a cikin Binciken Likita na Soja a ranar 06 ga Fabrairu 2020.
Ya jawo hankali sosai tun lokacin da aka buga shi.
Amma dai a lura da cewa COVID-19 sabuwar cuta ce, saninmu da iliminmu na kara ƙaruwa ne a hankali bisa ga binciken bincike da ake yi da kuma kwarewar aikin asibiti; saboda haka, dabarun ganewar asali da magani suma ana ci gaba da sabunta su.
Misali, Jagororin Bincike da Magani na COVID-19 da Kwamitin Lafiya na Kasa na Jamhuriyar Jama'ar Sin (http://www.nhc.gov.cn/), ya bayar tsakanin 16 ga Janairu 2020 zuwa 3 ga Maris 2020, ya bayar da jimillar bugu bakwai tare da wasu mahallin da aka canza sosai.
Yanzu jagorarmu ta sami tsokaci daga Zhou et al., sun gabatar da wata shawara mai sauƙi bisa ga kwarewarsu ta asibiti.
Aikin su ya kara sabbin shaidu ga ka'idarmu kuma ya kuma ba da muhimmin bayani game da wannan annoba a duniya.
Muna goyon bayan aikinsu mai muhimmanci kuma muna nuna godiyarmu.
Koyaya, aikin su kuma yana buƙatar sabuntawa bisa ga sabon Jagororin Bincike da Magani don COVID-19 (Trial na bakwai) da kuma binciken kwanan nan.
Dangane da bugu na bakwai (3 Maris 2020), don tabbatar da yanayin da ake zargi yana buƙatar haɗuwa da kowane ɗayan abubuwan tarihin cututtukan cututtukan cuta tare da abubuwa biyu na bayyanar cututtukan cututtukan cuta don yin cikakken bincike, ko kuma ya buƙaci biyan abubuwa uku na bayyanar cututtukan cututtukan cuta idan ba tare da bayyanannen tarihin cututtukan cuta ba:
Tarihin cututtukan cututtuka: (1) tarihin tafiya ko zama a birnin Wuhan da kewaye, ko wasu al'ummomi inda aka ba da rahoton COVID-19 a cikin kwanaki 14 da suka gabata kafin bayyanar cututtuka; (2) tarihin hulɗa da masu kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 (tare da gwajin sinadarin nucleic acid mai kyau); (3) tarihin hulɗa da marasa lafiya da ke da zazzabi ko alamun numfashi daga birnin Wuhan da kewaye, ko wasu al'ummomi inda aka ba da rahoton COVID-19 a cikin kwanaki 14 kafin bayyanar cututtuka; (4) tarihin hulɗa da tarin lokuta da aka tabbatar (≥ 2 da zazzabi da/ko alamun numfashi sun faru a cikin makonni 2 a ƙananan yankuna, kamar gida, ofis, aji na makaranta, da sauransu).
Bayyanar asibiti: (1) zazzabi da/ko alamun numfashi; (2) tare da alamun hoto na kamuwa da COVID-19; (3) jimlar adadin farin jini yana nuna al'ada, raguwa, ko rage ƙididdigar ƙwayoyin cuta a farkon matakin farawa.
Tabbatar da cutar da aka tabbatar ya kamata ya dogara da wanda ake zargi da cutar tare da kowane abu guda na pathogenic ko tabbacin serological kamar haka: (1) gwajin PCR na ainihin lokacin da ke nuna tabbatacce ga SARS-CoV-2; (2) jerin kwayoyin halittar kwayar cutar da ke nuna babban daidaituwa ga sanannun sabbin coronaviruses; (3) tabbatacce ga takamaiman IgM antibody da IgG antibody zuwa SARS-CoV-2 a cikin gwajin magani; ko canjin SARS-CoV-2-takamaiman IgG antibody daga mara kyau zuwa mai kyau, ko ƙimar da ke ƙaruwa sau ≥4 a cikin lokacin dawo da sama da na lokacin mai tsanani.
Muna iya ganin cewa an kara gwajin PCR na ainihin lokacin don nucleic acid a cikin hanyoyin numfashi ko samfurin jini a karo na biyu (18 ga Janairu 2020) da na uku (22 ga Janairu 2020).
An kara gano cututtukan cututtukan jini a cikin na huɗu (27 Janairu 2020) da na biyar (8 Fabrairu 2020); sannan kuma an kara shaidar kwayar cuta a cikin na bakwai.
Waɗannan gyare-gyare da aka yi dangane da masu binciken sun ci gaba da aiki don neman ingantaccen kayan gano sinadarin nucleic acid don saurin ganewar asali, da kuma samfuran daga hanyoyin numfashi ciki har da ɗaukar samfurin jini, wanda ya haɓaka kasancewar samfuran daban-daban, kuma ya goyi bayan kawo sakamakon ƙayyadaddun ƙwayar ƙwayar cuta a cikin ingantattun ƙa'idodi.
Bayan haka, akwai ƙarin shaidu da yawa da ke tunatar da mu mu yi hankali tare da marasa lafiya marasa alamun da marasa alamun.
Saboda haka, ya kamata a sabunta jadawalin kwararar Zhou et al. , kamar yadda suka rarraba mutumin da ba shi da alamun asibiti a matsayin  low risk .
Hakanan ana buƙatar tabbatar da ƙimar tsarin a cikin ƙarin aikin asibiti da bincike.
Don kammala, muna fatan ƙarin shaidar kai tsaye da ke zuwa kuma kira ga masu karatu don samar da ra'ayoyinsu.
Don tantance  wanda ake zargi  da  wanda aka tabbatar , muna ba da shawarar a gano da kuma bin sabbin ka'idojin ƙasashensu.
Tawagarmu za ta sabunta ka'idojinmu a kan lokaci don ba da taimako.
Bangladesh ta ba da rahoton sabbin mutuwar biyar saboda COVID-19, mafi girma a kowace rana
A jiya, Bangladesh ta tabbatar da sabbin mutuwar mutum biyar saboda COVID-19 a ranar.
Wannan shi ne adadi mafi yawa na mutuwar a rana guda saboda cutar.
Kamar yadda aka yi a jiya, Cibiyar Kula da cututtuka, Kula da cututtuka da Bincike ta Bangladesh (IEDCR) ta ba da rahoton adadin wadanda aka kamu da cutar da aka rubuta sun hada da mutane 114 da ke aiki da kuma 33 da suka warke wadanda ke zama a gida.
An yi rikodin jimillar mutuwar 17.
A wani taron manema labarai na yanar gizo, darektan IEDCR, Dr Meerjady Sabrina Flora, ya ce wadanda suka mutu sun hada da maza hudu da mace daya.
A cewar Dr. Meerjady, mutane biyu sun haura shekaru 60, biyu tsakanin 51 da 60, kuma daya yana da shekaru 41-50.
Ta kuma ce biyu daga cikin wadanda abin ya shafa 'yan Dhaka ne.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba a ranar 11 ga Maris.
Wani jami'in asibiti ya gaya wa kamfanin dillancin labarai na Anadolu, cewa daya daga cikin wadanda suka mutu shi ne Jalal Saifur Rahman, darektan Hukumar Yaki da Cin Hanci da Rashawa ta Bengali, wanda aka kula da shi a Asibitin Maitree na Kuwait.
