Wani binciken na Danish da aka gudanar a 2012 ya gano cewa yawan wanke hannu zai iya haifar da yanayin fata mai saurin fata da ake kira eczema ko dermatitis na hannu, wanda ya zama ruwan dare a tsakanin ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya.
Yin wanke hannu sau da yawa ana ganin shi ne daya daga cikin alamomin rashin lafiyar damuwa (OCD).
Akwai lokuta masu mahimmanci guda biyar a cikin rana inda wanke hannu da sabulu yana da mahimmanci don rage watsawar cutar ta hanyar fecal-oral: bayan amfani da banɗaki (urination, defecation), bayan tsabtace ƙasan yaro (canza diapers), kafin ciyar da yaro, kafin cin abinci da kafin / bayan shirya abinci ko sarrafa ɗanyen nama, kifi, ko kaji.
