b'Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) wani enzyme ne wanda aka haɗe da farfajiyar waje (cells membranes) na ƙwayoyin cuta a cikin huhu, jijiyoyin jini, zuciya, koda, da kuma hanji.
ACE2 yana magance aikin angiotensin-converting enzyme (ACE) ta hanyar rage adadin angiotensin-II da haɓaka Ang ((1-7) yana mai da shi wata manufa mai kyau ta magani don magance cututtukan zuciya. ACE2 kuma yana aiki a matsayin shigarwa cikin ƙwayoyin don wasu coronaviruses.
Ana kiran nau'in ɗan adam na enzyme sau da yawa azaman hACE2.
Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 wani zinc ne mai dauke da metallol enzyme wanda yake a saman endothelial da sauran kwayoyin halitta.
Furotin ACE2 ya ƙunshi yankin peptidase M2 na N-terminal da kuma yankin C-terminal na mai ɗaukar amino acid mai ɗaukar koda.
ACE2 shine furotin membrane mai wucewa guda ɗaya, tare da yankin da ke da enzyme mai aiki wanda aka fallasa a saman ƙwayoyin cuta a cikin huhu da sauran ƙwayoyin.
An raba yankin da ke cikin ACE2 daga yankin transmembrane ta wani enzyme da ake kira sheddase, kuma ana fitar da furotin mai narkewa zuwa cikin jini kuma a ƙarshe an fitar dashi cikin fitsari.
