ACE tana raba angiotensin I hormone zuwa cikin angiotensin II mai hana jijiyoyin jini.
ACE2 a bi da bi yana rarraba amino acid carboxyl-terminal phenylalanine daga angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) kuma yana shayar da shi zuwa angiotensin (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 kuma na iya raba wasu peptides da suka hada da [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dynorphin A, da ghrelin.
