A matsayin furotin na transmembrane, ACE2 yana aiki a matsayin babban wurin shiga cikin ƙwayoyin cuta don wasu coronaviruses, gami da HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (kwayar cutar da ke haifar da SARS); da SARS-CoV-2 (kwayar cutar da ke haifar da COVID-19).
